e":{"pid":"f65b6b12b82ccc6c1f34a7ec3006b246e76d3a40","tid":1143174,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"暑期青少年刑事偵緝調查技巧初級証書課程<br />\n原來依家有d咁既堂上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"一定係退休黑警教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:12:42.000Z","msg":"課程內容包括：<br />\n(1) 查問疑犯、盤問技巧及錄取口供技巧；(2) 接待證人、受害人的應有態度；<br />\n(3) 罪案趨勢和偵緝調查方法；<br />\n(4) 處理現場及證物的正確程序；<br />\n(5) 罪行定義、法例及其應用；<br />\n(6) 罪案調查及罪惡活動；<br />\n(7) 嚴重罪案及黑社會案件；<br />\n(8) 調查報告及檔案編輯；<br />\n(9) 刑事司法制度及司法機構；<br />\n(10) 法醫科。<br />\n   本課程由前紀律部隊資深刑事偵緝調查人員執教。<br />\n<br />\n唔知之後有沒中級同高級讀<br />\n提早培養青少年做警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4b14e94240d8bdb3400a60ff102f1315b095a7","tid":1143174,"uid":135722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"想報 但係會唔會成場都係啊叔啊嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fa2a319562aed06405ea010e30c55f872d5c3c","tid":1143174,"uid":16743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"麵包班打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今期學中班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0152eaba1b4a18da5631b8cc2128b94bb37753a3","tid":1143174,"uid":192432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4b14e94240d8bdb3400a60ff102f1315b095a7","tid":1143174,"uid":135722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"想報 但係會唔會成場都係啊叔啊嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:00:53.000Z","msg":"我都驚緊"},{"pid":"b0730770390a52cf8220ddd6dc91b1a5db43e1ab","tid":1143174,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q